Senate Bill 340
By: Senator Watson of the 1st
AS PASSED
A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend an Act to provide for a new charter for the City of Tybee Island, approved
2 April 20, 1995 (Ga. L. 1995, p. 4462), as amended, particularly by an Act approved April 2,
3 2019 (Ga. L. 2019, p. 3569), so as to provide for the selection of a mayor pro tem; to provide
4 for the duties of the mayor pro tem; to provide for filling a vacancy in the office of the mayor
5 pro tem; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 An Act to provide for a new charter for the City of Tybee Island, approved April 20, 1995
9 (Ga. L. 1995, p. 4462), as amended, particularly by an Act approved April 2, 2019 (Ga. L.
10 2019, p. 3569), is amended by revising Section 2.33 as follows:
11 "SECTION 2.33.
12 Selection and powers and duties of the mayor pro tem.
13 At the first regular meeting of the city council following a regular election and the
14 assumption of office by the newly elected city council members, the city council shall
